<template><div><h1 id="accessing-orchestrated-application-recovery" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#accessing-orchestrated-application-recovery" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Accessing Orchestrated Application Recovery</h1>
<h2 id="orchestrated-application-recovery" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#orchestrated-application-recovery" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Orchestrated Application Recovery</h2>
<p>Orchestrated application recovery is delivered as a Rubrik Security Cloud-based application. It provides orchestration of DR failover/failback, testing, and together with application-focused Ransomware Investigation, which will radically simplify recovery for business services running in VMware vSphere environments. As a result, IT organizations can eliminate multiple-point solutions and management complexity and avoid unnecessary costs.</p>
<h2 id="accessing-orchestrated-application-recovery-1" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#accessing-orchestrated-application-recovery-1" aria-hidden="true">#</a> Accessing Orchestrated Application Recovery</h2>
<p>If you haven't already connected to the Rubrik Security Cloud, head back to the <RouterLink to="/pages/lab_environment/lab-0.html">lab environment</RouterLink>.</p>
<p>Once you're logged in, click the app-tray icon in the top right of the user interface, then select <strong>Application Recovery</strong>.</p>
<p><img src="@source/pages/orchestrated_recovery/images/access-OAR.gif" alt="Launch Orchestrated Application Recovery from the app-tray"></p>
